{"tid":1689050,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"［教學］如何做一個真正的上街和理非","createTime":"2019-11-02T16:09:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-02T16:11:15.000Z","uid":89627,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"7fe393ab0c02ff1fdb8339d4f30e86747182d1f7","tid":1689050,"uid":89627,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T16:09:49.000Z","msg":"勇武已經由6月開始進化，但和理非仍然好似停濟不前咁！<br />\n<br />\n首先好多謝咁多位和理非到今時今日仲肯出黎上街遊行！<br />\n<br />\n但希望你地心態上都要跟著改變，要明白到而家遊行唔係講玩，唔係只係大叫 「香港人反抗！」就算，大家上得街就要預咗被人拉，坐48小時<br />\n<br />\n唔好再因爲少少事/甚至唔知咩事，就唔理3721就跑走啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n上一秒就好大聲講香港人反抗，下一秒就跑走.....<br />\n今日班狗見到咁既場面，應該笑咗出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n希望如果下次再有遊行(唔好再喺港島啦)，後排既和理非們心態上都可以做到！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5e5b2f241e589fe813205e009b8cca2232589b75","tid":1689050,"uid":263058,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-02T16:11:15.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"}]}